  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MetIri seeks to identify if metformin combined to irinotecan can improve tumor control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      MetIri is a two-stage single arm Phase II assessing the role of combination of metformin to
      irinotecan for colorectal cancer patients already treat with oxaliplatin, fluoropyrimidine,
      irinotecan and an anti-EGFr antibody if KRAS wild-type.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
